spx.utils

Interface SystemHealthSrc


  • public interface SystemHealthSrc
    Definitions for the source status values (top byte of 16-bit value, the bottom byte is source-specific), used in the sourceStatus field of a Heartbeat.

    These constants are kept in sync with the SPX_SYSTEM_HEALTH_SRC... constants in "SPxSystemHealth.h".

    See Also:
    Heartbeat
